OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of mostly
OL,6,Flight rain clearing eastward, with
OL,7,Fdrier and brighter intervals
OL,8,Fdeveloping from around midday.
OL,9,FHowever, heavy showery rain arriving
OL,10,Fin the west later in the afternoon.
OL,11,FMild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome early evening bright
OL,14,Fspells possible in the south and east
OL,15,Fbefore cloud and rain, heavy at times,
OL,16,Fspreads to all parts through the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
